title: Episode Eight: Dulé Hill - Who Ya Gonna Call
description:
We're back with another episode of "The Psychologists Are In!" This week we chat with the incredible Dulé Hill - the Dean Martin to Roday's Jerry Lewis.

Today we talk wardrobe fails, unaired scenes, and the supernatural - while we listen to "Dulé Dropping Wisdom" - the runner up title of this episode.
